===Etymology===
[[Neologism]] coined in 2003 as a blend of [[apathy]] (see article for full etymology) and [[theism]] (from {{Gr.}} ''[[θεός]] (Theós) "god").

===Noun===
{{en-noun|-}}
# apathy towards the existence of [[God]]; belief that the question of the existence of [[God]] is unimportant

